{"root":{"data":{"id":"djhqcvki16o0","created":1782350037521,"text":"报告与审核审计"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djhqdphgxg00","created":1782350102641,"text":"现场检查报告（ON SITE CHECKING REPORT）","layout_mind_offset":{"x":1.9999987185001658,"y":-95.99999856948855}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djhqnkx44c00","created":1782350876345,"text":"工厂（Factory）\n报告日期（Report Date）\n检查员（Inspector）\n描述（Description）","layout_right_offset":{"x":26.99999959766876,"y":-10.999999836087397}},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"djhqnz050sg0","created":1782350907004,"text":"A.Description 描述\nB.\nB.1\nB.2\n\nC.Conclusion 结论","layout_right_offset":{"x":30.999999538064117,"y":5.999999910592976}},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"djhra16a5yw0","created":1782352635739,"text":"Coach（word）","layout_mind_offset":{"x":-6.74999187141708,"y":48.499999389052505}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djhrbuhnp8g0","created":1782352777918,"text":"Belt EP Application","layout_right_offset":{"x":63.74999810010212,"y":-59.99999821186083}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djhrwdu2wlc0","created":1782354387311,"text":"Audited Service Provider\nDate & Time\nAuditor\nTitle\n\nScoring System（\n0：Nothing in place; \n1：Ver basic/simple system in place; \n2:  Comprehensice system in place with scope for considerable improvement \n3:  Good comprehensive system in place that needs fine tuning/perfecting \n4：Very good, comprehensive & up to date system in place\n）\nLogic: Final Result = Rate/Max. Scores (Max.Scores= # of Checking Points ×4)\n\nTable \n\nPart Name\n\nConclusion","layout_right_offset":{"x":127.49999620020412,"y":-8.749999739229736}},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"djhs88c85s80","created":1782355315718,"text":"Table","layout_right_offset":{"x":106.24999683350325,"y":38.74999884515978}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djhs8nfuoyw0","created":1782355348589,"text":"1、No.\n2、Description\n3、Using applicators & Processing\n4、Score\n5、Remarks","layout_right_offset":{"x":86.24999742954992,"y":4.999999850988274}},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"djhscx7ukq80","created":1782355683329,"text":"1、Leather Edge Preparation before apply promoter or Edge Paint\n2、Application Process（SOP）\n3、Apply Promoter - UA400H\n4、Apply Primer - CA220R1\n5、Apply Edge Paint - CHS330R1、CHM339R1、DAH630\n6、Drying\n7、Buffing\n8、Polishing\n9、Final appearance\n10、Workers' proficiency\n11、Painted parts before moving to the next production stage","layout_right_offset":{"x":78.749997653067,"y":133.7499960139395}},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"djhruujgudc0","created":1782354266947,"text":"EP Storage, Prepare and Handling","layout_right_offset":{"x":109.99999672174471,"y":207.49999381601833}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djht1etc29c0","created":1782357602375,"text":"1、SOP and others guiding for the storage condition is available in Ware house and workshop edge paint storage area\n2、Always keep primer / edge paint at temperature 5℃-30℃ @ 40%-70% Humidity in the warehouse\n3、Keep the Promoter, Primer and Edge Paint away from direct sunlight\n4、Ware house is kept well ventilated\n5、All products must be put on the pallets or shelves for storage\n6、All drums or pails must be closed very well during the storage","layout_right_offset":{"x":159.99999523162842,"y":-13.749999590218067}},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"djht853n0k00","created":1782358129778,"text":"分支主题","layout_right_offset":{"x":21.24999936670065,"y":3.749999888241291}},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"djht19iichs0","created":1782357590835,"text":"Handbag EP Application\nWallet & SLG EP Application","layout_right_offset":{"x":53.749998398125285,"y":341.24998982995794}},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"djhra4ao7eg0","created":1782352642535,"text":"Michael Kors（excel）","layout_mind_offset":{"x":646.2499807402494,"y":1219.9999636411671}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djhrbuhnp8g0","created":1782352777918,"text":"Belt Application\nHandbag Application\nStorage\nWallet Application","layout_right_offset":{"x":16.249999515712318,"y":-18.7499994412064}},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"djhrb3uhoe80","created":1782352719921,"text":"Tory Burch（excel）","layout_mind_offset":{"x":637.4999810010199,"y":1322.4999605864293}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djhrpeoysts0","created":1782353840630,"text":"Handbag Application\nStorage\nWallet Application","layout_right_offset":{"x":32.49999903142452,"y":-36.2499989196657}},"children":[]}]}]},"template":"default","theme":"fresh-blue","version":"1.4.43"}